article_title: Walgreens Expands Doctor Access Via Telehealth To 25 States

article_metadata.description: VideoWalgreens Boots Alliance (WBA), working with telemedicine company MDLive, will expand round-the-clock access to physicians via digital device for customers in 25 states by the end of the year. The announcement by the nation’s largest drugstore chain comes as the health care industry invests in a variety of ways to expand virtual doctor [...]
